# === Security Absolute Barrier ===
# 機密情報、個人データ、ローカル環境依存ファイルは絶対に弾く

# 1. Environment & Secrets
.env
*.env
secret*
credentials.json
token.json
ag_secret_manager.py

# 2. Local Logs & Temp Data
*.log
temp/
logs/
*.json
*.sqlite
*.db

# 3. OS Generated Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# 4. IDE / Cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.vscode/
.idea/

# 5. Local Deployment Scripts
deploy_to_github.bat
